{
  "title": "Spicy Velvety Middle Eastern Avocado Stir-fry",
  "description": "This dish combines the smooth texture of avocado with the spicy kick from Middle Eastern spices in a one-pot gluten-free recipe that's perfect for a quick and easy dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
